google.description: Dancing with the enemy Krish Dev needs to find a bride—and quick! With a marriage arranged by his father looming, Krish finds the key to his freedom in Maya Shome. But is this dazzling beauty really all she seems…? Maya has only one thing in mind: revenge. But when the host of the most exclusive high society party asks her to dance what is meant to be an innocent tango, it leads to an engagement to Krish—her enemy's son! Arranging their own marriage could work to their advantage…if they can resist mixing business with pleasure!
google.title: The Indian Tycoon's Marriage Deal
